Are both of your commands in your parallel group ending? if not it will not move on. You can use a deadline group and the first one you put in there will end both when it ends. We will run deadline groups with a follow path as the deadline and an intake note command with it so that when it gets to the end of the path it ends the intake command. You could also add a .withtimeout to the commands not ending so they only run so long
